      <tr><td><b>PE / dPE</b></td><td>Control-board communication</td><td>Harness reseat first, board if persists</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p>Service Mode access differs by LG generation, 2018+ SmartThinQ models show real-time temperature + diagnostic data via LG ThinQ app (factory-service-only feature set). Pre-2018 models use a button-hold sequence on the control panel (generation-specific). We carry the factory sequences on dispatch tablet.</p>
